<div class="e-ease ee:wwig" id="_accreditations" style="text-align: center;"><img alt="" class="img-responsive" src="/apps/_ee/files/goldseal_4color.jpg" style="width: 200px; height: 200px; margin: 0px auto;" /></div>  <div class="e-ease ee:wwig" style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div>  <div class="e-ease ee:wwig" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#3399cc;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times,serif;">The Joint Commission&rsquo;s Gold Seal of Approval&trade;</span></span></span> </strong>- for Nursing Care Center Accreditation and the organization&rsquo;s new Post-Acute Care Certification demonstrate a nursing center&rsquo;s commitment to the highest level of care for its patients and residents&mdash;going beyond state and federal requirements.</div>  <div class="e-ease ee:wwig" style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div>  <div class="e-ease ee:wwig" style="text-align: center;"> <div class="btgrid"> <div class="row row-1"> <div class="col col-md-4"> <div class="content"> <p><img alt="" class="img-responsive" src="/apps/_ee/files/bnh2014logofinal.png" style="width: 250px; height: 182px; margin: 0px auto;" /></p> </div> </div>  <div class="col col-md-4"> <div class="content"> <p><img alt="" class="img-responsive" src="/apps/_ee/files/bnh2015logofinal.png" style="width: 250px; height: 187px; margin: 0px auto;" /></p> </div> </div>  <div class="col col-md-4"> <div class="content"> <p><img alt="" class="img-responsive" src="/apps/_ee/files/bnh2016logofinal.png" style="width: 250px; height: 182px; margin: 0px auto;" /></p> </div> </div> </div> </div>  <p><span style="color:#3399cc;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>The U.S. News &amp; World Report annual rankings </strong></span></span></span>- to help U.S. residents select a nursing home. For the rankings, U.S. News used data from CMS&#39;s Nursing Home Compare website&mdash;which considers findings from health inspections, evaluations of the nursing staff, and performance on quality measures&mdash;and awarded &quot;Best Nursing Homes&quot; status to facilities that earned the agency&#39;s five stars.</p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p><img alt="" class="img-responsive" src="/apps/_ee/files/massseniorassociation.jpg" style="width: 250px; height: 225px; margin: 0px auto;" /><br /> <span style="color:#3399cc;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>The Massachusetts Senior Care Association</strong></span></span></span> - represents a diverse set of organizations that deliver a broad spectrum of services to meet the needs of older adults and people with disabilities.&nbsp; Our members include more than 500 nursing and rehabilitation facilities, assisted living residences, residential care facilities and continuing care retirement communities.</p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p><img alt="" class="shadow img-responsive" src="/apps/_ee/files/aurumlogo1.jpg" style="width: 750px; height: 220px; margin: 0px auto;" /><br /> <span style="color:#3399cc;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>The Aurum Network</strong></span></span></span> - established in 1997, is a cooperative alliance made up recognized leaders and industry standard-setters senior-care industry. Members utilize and share their technical expertise, leadership skills, best practices and problem-solving experiences in order to advance the network&rsquo;s gold standard of care and consistently improve the services they present to consumers.</p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <div class="btgrid"> <div class="row row-1"> <div class="col col-md-6"> <div class="content"> <p><img alt="" src="/apps/_ee/files/5-stars.png" style="width: 177px; height: 104px;" /></p> </div> </div>  <div class="col col-md-6"> <div class="content"> <p><img alt="" src="/apps/_ee/files/perfect-survey.png" style="width: 130px; height: 130px;" /></p> </div> </div> </div> </div>  <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color:#3399cc;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>Other Awards</strong></span></span></span>&nbsp;</p> </div> 